        "zh": "1.導論<br>2.閱讀的功能與樂趣<br>3.書寫與表達基本原理<br>4.中文各項文類評析<br>5.文學作品中各項人生議題之探討<br>6.實用文書基本能力<br>7.聽說讀寫綜合表達訓練",
        "en": "1. Introduction<br>2. The function and pleasure of reading<br>3. The basic principle in writing and expression<br>4. Evaluates all kind of Chinese literature type<br>5. The discussion of life issues in literary work<br>6. Practical word processing ability<br>7. The expression training: Hearing、speaking、reading and writing"
